Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:07.32,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\shad0\bord2\frz1.5\fs34\t(\fs32)\move(364.797,35,364.797,54,24,7323)\c&&HC9D4D7&}Warning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:03.10,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Viewers Sitting in Front of the Television,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.10,0:00:05.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,the guys that appear in this anime are delinquents.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.27,0:00:07.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So, please do not imitate what you see in this anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:09.98,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fnAveria Sans\b1\i0\bord0\blur0.3\fad(450,0)\c&HDADADA&\fs33\pos(362.532,49)}Do not imitate{\i1\fs40}!{\i0\fs33} Or this will happen{\i1\fs40}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)\an8}僕が泣いているのは とても悔しいからです
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Boku ga naite iru no wa totemo kuyashii kara desu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}The reason I am crying is\Nbecause I am very frustrated
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}人の尊さやさしさ 踏みにじられそうで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Hito no toutosa yasashisa fuminijiraresou de
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}I feel as though the nobility and\Nkindness of man is being trampled
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:31.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}力を示す者達は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:31.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Chikara o shimesu mono tachi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.51,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}しなやかさを失って
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.51,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Shinayakasa o ushinatte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:34.51,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Those who show their strength lose their grace
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.06,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}ウソまみれドロまみれ じれったい風景でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.06,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Uso-mamire doro-mamire jirettai fuukei desho
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.06,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Covered in dirt and lies, isn't it a vexing sight?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:45.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}より強くしたたかに タフな生き方をしましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:45.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Yori tsuyoku shitataka ni tafu na ikikata o shimashou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:45.35,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Let's live more strongly, fiercely, and tougher
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}まっすぐ歩きましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Massugu arukimasho
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Let's walk straight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.94,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}風は向かい風
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.94,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Kaze wa mukai kaze
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.94,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}The wind is against us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.40,0:00:58.78,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}どけ どけ どけ 後ろめたい奴はどけ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.40,0:00:58.78,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Doke doke doke ushirometai yatsu wa doke
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.40,0:00:58.78,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Move, move, move, those with\Na guilty conscience, move aside
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:03.41,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}有象無象の町に 灯りをともせ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:03.41,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Uzoumuzou no machi ni akari o tomose
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:03.41,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Light up the town of riffraff
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:08.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}どけ そこ どけ 真実のお通りだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:08.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Doke soko doke shinjitsu no otouri da
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:08.88,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Move, make way, truth is coming through
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}正義の時代がくるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Seigi no jidai ga kuru sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}The era of justice will come
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.55,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}希望の歌もあるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.55,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Kibou no uta mo aru sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.55,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}There are songs of hope too
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)\an8}僕の命この世に 捧げてしまっていいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)\an8}Boku no inochi kono yo ni sasagete-shimatte ii sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.35,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)}I would happily sacrifice my life for this world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.02,0:01:32.32,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2}Maeda's house
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.61,0:01:35.40,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday scumbag
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.74,0:01:38.45,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday to you, man
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.78,0:01:43.33,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday dear Maeda
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.20,0:01:46.87,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\fs26\shad0\frz359.349\c&H61696A&\3c&HE3EBEC&\fnDupree\b0\pos(358,27)\bord0}Happy Birthday
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.20,0:01:46.87,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\shad0\bord1.5\an8\p1\c&HE3EAED&\3c&H28353F&\pos(358,0)\be2}m 0 0 l 150 0 150 30 0 30{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.33,0:01:46.37,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday to you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.87,0:01:49.92,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,All right! I'm gonna go crazy today!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.92,0:01:52.21,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second, Hayashida.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.21,0:01:54.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's nice to be casual,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.01,0:01:57.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but this is Maeda's house,\Nso we'd better restrain ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.47,0:01:59.14,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No, that's okay, Kamiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.14,0:02:00.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:03.77,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Because you all got together for me today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.77,0:02:05.89,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You're really a nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.89,0:02:07.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm glad that we're close friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.73,0:02:09.10,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's my line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.10,0:02:12.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm really feeling happy today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.61,0:02:16.61,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,These guys always gather at my house\Nfor a "decide the strongest man meeting"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.61,0:02:20.37,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,or unimportant events\N I don't understand, without asking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.37,0:02:22.16,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's really been a bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.16,0:02:26.58,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But they gathered today\Nto celebrate my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:28.62,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There's no reason for me to get upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.62,0:02:30.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Even if they go crazy today, I'll let it slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:33.25,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But there's just one thing\N that I wanna say to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.89,0:02:43.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,My birthday was last month.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.97,0:02:45.35,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.81,0:02:50.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But if I said something like that,\Nit would only ruin the atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.06,0:02:52.65,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,They just made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:54.82,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I know for sure that\N they didn't do it on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:56.57,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm totally changing the subject,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:02:59.95,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but I heard there's an idol's autograph session \Nat the bookstore near the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:03.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Why don't we finish up\N Maeda's birthday early and head there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.49,0:03:05.16,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's fine too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.95,0:03:07.62,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So that's okay, right, Maeda?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:11.17,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Let me tell you something...\NThat's Maeda's old lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.58,0:03:12.79,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What are you guys saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.79,0:03:15.96,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Didn't you gather today\Nto celebrate my birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:17.67,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, that's what I wanna say,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.67,0:03:21.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but technically it's not my birthday today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.05,0:03:23.34,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to say anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.72,0:03:24.76,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hayashida...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:28.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, jerk?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.47,0:03:30.81,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This is the second time\N I've hit someone in my entire life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:33.52,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That shows how upset I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:37.11,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Even if it is among close friends,\Nthere's things you can say and things you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.11,0:03:40.65,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If you really cared about Maeda,\Nyou wouldn't have said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:41.99,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Hayashida?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:47.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's enough, Kamiyama. I don't mind at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:52.21,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No, Kamiyama's right.\N I got carried away and said a stupid thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.21,0:03:55.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Sometimes careless words hurt \Nother people's feelings, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.88,0:03:57.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Maeda. Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:04:00.72,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Stop it! This isn't like the Hayashida I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.72,0:04:04.72,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay, all settled then.\N Now let's start again from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:06.89,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Actually we have a present for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.89,0:04:09.14,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This is a specially made cake, Maeda.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:12.89,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You're the star today. Now blow out the candles.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:15.23,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Thanks, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:17.02,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll blow them out in one breath.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.02,0:04:21.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\shad0\frz359.349\c&H61696A&\3c&HE3EBEC&\fnDupree\b0\pos(358,27)\bord0}Happy Birthday
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.73,0:04:20.28,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:21.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord1.5\an8\p1\c&HE3EAED&\3c&H28353F&\pos(358,0)\be2}m 0 0 l 150 0 150 30 0 30{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.73,0:04:19.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Maeda, happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:21.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday, Maeda!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:23.45,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's my old lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.45,0:04:24.91,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(356.867,394)}A few days later
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:27.95,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There's someone that\N I want to introduce to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.95,0:04:29.16,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What? Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:31.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This is my little brother, Beta Mechazawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:31.54,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fnGilles' Comic Font\fs38\bord0\blur0.5\b1\shad0\c&H120F17&\pos(689.943,290)}Guts
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.54,0:04:32.96,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fnGilles' Comic Font\fs28\bord0\blur0.5\b1\shad0\c&H120F17&\pos(471.291,319)}Guts
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.91,0:04:32.96,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Mecha-ratta.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.79,0:04:35.71,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Mechazawa's little brother, he said?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.71,0:04:38.59,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's not good to bring your\N little brother to school, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.59,0:04:41.67,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No, I don't think that's\N the surprising part, Hayashida.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.67,0:04:45.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I heard that he's really good at fighting,\Ndespite his appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:47.55,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I guess you could say he's resilient.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:51.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Just what you'd expect\N from someone related to me by blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:53.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I see, I think I understand what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:56.81,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Shall we try having him fight\N one-on-one with someone? Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.77,0:05:01.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.07,0:05:04.07,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(356.867,394)}A few days later
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:04.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Mechazawa's little brother finally got fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.53,0:05:07.37,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Wow! They fixed him up real good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.37,0:05:09.95,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The people at Sato Electronics\Nreally are pretty skilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:12.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But isn't he smaller than before?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:15.25,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I think it's okay, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.25,0:05:18.21,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The newer the cell phones are,\Nthe smaller they get too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.09,0:05:21.59,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, what happened\Nto his older brother, Mechazawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.59,0:05:24.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, I heard that the incident\Ncame as a huge shock to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.05,0:05:27.59,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,so he ended up confining himself to his bed.\NIf anything, I'm kinda more worried about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:31.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, I just thought of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:34.48,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If he's with us, we won't lose a fight\Nno matter how strong our enemy is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:37.52,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,How in the heck can we win fights using him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:38.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Let me see him for a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:41.57,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We can win fights like this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:44.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If we're throwing something,\Nwe can throw just rocks or balls!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:45.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,And he's dented again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:50.16,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Of course I'm against\N using him as a fighting tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:54.29,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But if you're going to use him,\Nyou have to fully use his abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:58.83,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Exactly! Use your head more.\NHe's more or less intelligent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:06:01.92,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,And he can also walk\N and his body is small.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:04.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That means there's only one way\Nwe can use him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:05.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:06.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Spying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:07.59,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Spying...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.59,0:06:10.85,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But far from picking up information as a spy,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.85,0:06:14.35,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,there's a risk that he'll be picked up\Nby someone and taken home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.35,0:06:17.69,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.\N I'll teach him about those kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:19.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Education is important for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.73,0:06:22.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If I teach him from the ground up,\Nwithin a month he'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.06,0:06:23.57,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hokuto, eyes down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:24.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:28.90,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This isn't working at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.90,0:06:33.03,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2}Next day
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:31.20,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,478)}Mechazawa's saying that since\Nhe got better without a hitch,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.20,0:06:33.03,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,he wants to come and get his little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:34.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What're we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.49,0:06:38.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The Sato Electronics person told me that fixing\Nhis little brother would take until tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.04,0:06:40.08,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Mechazawa loves his little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:42.71,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I think he'll certainly get angry when he finds out\Nthat his little brother got broken again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:45.55,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I can just see his angry face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:47.38,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Not that his expression changes much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:49.34,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, why do you always gather at my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.34,0:06:50.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I have a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:53.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Give me that tea caddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:56.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Here, done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.22,0:06:58.35,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, to say the least, this isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.35,0:07:00.85,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If we put it far away like this, he wouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:02.61,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If we can weasel our way\N through today, it'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.61,0:07:03.61,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I wonder if this'll work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:06.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Listen, don't ever talk about his little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.98,0:07:10.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Even if he starts talking about his little brother,\Ndo everything you can to avoid it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:12.20,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Isn't that Mechazawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:15.16,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Sorry for being late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.16,0:07:16.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We've been waiting for you. Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:19.16,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, it's great to see you got better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.16,0:07:21.62,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry that I worried you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.62,0:07:24.17,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,By the way, where's my little brother Beta?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:26.67,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He's all right. He's sitting here just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.67,0:07:29.92,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, forget about that and\Nmake yourself at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:31.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You're a nice guy, Hayashida.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:35.72,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You seem rough, but you're\Nactually very considerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:36.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You're embarrassing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:39.60,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If you say that, well, I guess\NI'll have to be considerate then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.60,0:07:41.02,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'll make some tea now, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:44.19,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\c&H151114&\3c&H3D409F&\bord3\be3\t(\fs56)\frz300.746\move(466.759,415,428.241,344,27,1945)}Fury
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.40,0:07:44.77,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What happened to my little brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:46.61,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He's in the hospital right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:47.23,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,At Sato Electronics Store...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:50.78,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,How dare you mess with me,\Nswitching him with a tea caddy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:52.57,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He isn't much different from a tea caddy, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:53.95,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hayashida, you're going too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:56.45,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You'd better stop making\Na fool out of me, moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:58.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Your yapping is really annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.00,0:08:04.25,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The data has just been formatted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.25,0:08:05.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,0:08:07.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's going too far, Hayashida!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:09.96,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Put him in the closet for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.96,0:08:12.13,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If my old lady finds out, I'll be scolded.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.13,0:08:13.63,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2}Next day
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.14,0:08:16.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,His little brother, Beta, was repaired safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:20.14,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I like him better, because\Nit's easy to deal with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:21.60,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.60,0:08:22.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.73,0:08:24.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Everyone's acting normal,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.56,0:08:28.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but to start with, what the hell\Nis this Mechazawa family?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.27,0:08:30.99,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, there's no use discussing this right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.99,0:08:33.74,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No, isn't now the time to discuss it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:35.78,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,His little brother's also in the picture now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:37.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If we don't, it's gonna drag on like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:41.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Where's their house? Do they have parents?\NOr more importantly, who created them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.54,0:08:42.79,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There are lots of questions, aren't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.79,0:08:44.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Who created them? Hey, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.50,0:08:46.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Why doesn't anyone say it straight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:48.13,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Because no matter how you look at them,\Nthey're definitely robo...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:52.67,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Don't say any more!\N What you are about to say is bashing Mechazawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:54.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Listen. We're badasses,\Nbut we don't bash others.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:56.30,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Bear that in mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:09:00.18,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay. I won't talk about it any more.\NThen let me say my name...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.18,0:09:01.72,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No, I don't wanna hear that either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.72,0:09:05.10,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But the Mechazawa family's true identity\Nis something that weighs on my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:09.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's possible that he came\N to our school with some sort of goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.06,0:09:12.99,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There's no way that such a small,\Ntoy-like thing has a goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.99,0:09:14.45,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You're thinking too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.45,0:09:17.45,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But even for cell phones, the more\Nadvanced they are, the smaller they get.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:20.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's possible that even this thing\N may have amazing capabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.49,0:09:21.99,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.99,0:09:24.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Don't compare everything with cell phones.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:27.79,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's a ring tone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:29.92,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Is it really a cell phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:32.13,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,More like, who's calling?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:33.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Anyhow, someone answer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:36.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You gotta be kidding.\NThat's creepy, I can't answer it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:37.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yes, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:39.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,K-Kamiyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.26,0:09:44.31,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes... I see... Got it... Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.31,0:09:45.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Who was it from?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.56,0:09:47.02,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, it was a wrong number.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.02,0:09:48.90,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hang up on those right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:50.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's ringing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:52.53,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,All right, then, I'll answer this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.53,0:09:53.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We're counting on you, Hayashida.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:55.28,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yes, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:09:57.11,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What?! Got it! We'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:09:58.16,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:10:00.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That was from Maeda!\NIt seems something's happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.07,0:10:01.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He asked us to come to his house.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:05.45,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It must be big if Maeda himself\Nasked us to come to his house.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:07.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What I wanna know is, \Nwhere was he calling from?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:10.38,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\fnMaiandra GD\fs36\c&HA7A2AA&\3c&H282935&\bord4\frx34\fry56\frz324.509\pos(360.266,180)}Maeda
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:10.92,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I was just cleaning the closet, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.92,0:10:12.09,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:12.96,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He isn't here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:16.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This is a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:19.34,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In addition, he disappeared\N after such a short time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.34,0:10:20.89,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Did he start walking by himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.89,0:10:23.10,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Could it be that he got \Nthrown out as oversized trash?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:24.68,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Anyway, calm down, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.68,0:10:26.81,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If we act rashly,\N we'll make matters worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.10,0:10:28.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He's right. Let's calm down a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.98,0:10:31.65,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Let's have some tea and think about it\Ncalmly for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.94,0:10:35.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, there's some iced tea in the fridge there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:37.61,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay, the fridge there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.61,0:10:39.15,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hello. Please excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.15,0:10:41.57,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. Can I have a glass of iced tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:45.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's the one! That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:45.01,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\alpha130\fs24\fnNeon\bord0\c&H4E1728&\blur0.5\pos(346.671,139)}Next\N\N\N\NEpisode
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.01,0:11:50.02,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fs26\blur0.5\fnArial Black\bord3\c&H000000&\3c&HFBFAFC&\pos(203.924,50)}Sakigake!!\NCromartie High School
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:50.02,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fs26\blur0.6\fnArial Black\bord3.2\c&H000000&\3c&H3F3F3F&\pos(203.924,50)}Sakigake!!\NCromartie High School
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:50.02,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial Black\shad0\fs36\bord2.2\blur0.5\pos(446.367,391)}Next episode, Jackson
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.67,0:11:37.21,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.21,0:11:38.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Sakigake!! Cromartie High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.88,0:11:41.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This was supposed to be the time\Nto announce the next episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.63,0:11:43.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't do such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:43.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:48.35,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It could've been my old lady's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:49.68,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If so, that's the right answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:07.32,Intro Warning,,0,0,0,,{\fs23\blur0.3\pos(213.928,323.39)}When you are watching television
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:07.32,Intro Warning,,0,0,0,,{\fs23\blur0.3\pos(587.096,341.559)}please have the room\Nbrightly lit and be\Ncareful not to get too\Nclose to the screen.
